[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Do you think it would be feasible to link the right to vote to rehabilitation?  For example, providing prisoners with an opportunity to be educated in civic responsibility and, as part of this, allowing them to apply to be enfranchised? 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Enfranchisement c
[normal]ould 
[normal]certain
[normal]ly be of value in supporting offenders’ 
[normal]reintegration. 
[normal]But we cannot say whether a 
[normal]scheme 
[normal]of this sort would be practical. Those who might feel strongly about being disenfranchised may not regard such a scheme as having any legitimacy. 
[normal]&#xa0;
