[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]How easily could sentencing guidelines incorporate an ancillary penalty of disenfranchisement on an individual basis? 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]In our view relatively easily, although this is a question for the Sentencing Council to answer
[normal].
